Preheat oven to 350 degrees F (175 degrees C). Mix together oatmeal, baking soda, chocolate chips, M & M's , and peanuts. Set aside. In a separate bowl, mix together white sugar, brown sugar, butter or margarine, vanilla, eggs and peanut butter. Combine the two mixes. Wet your hands. Roll into 1 inch balls. Bake on a greased cookie sheet for 10 to 12 minutes.